title: How an Ecuadorian ended up volunteering in Čadca
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Ecuadorian Jorge Mancero, who is helping a community in northern Slovakia, sat down with Peter to talk about Čadca, Slovakia and Ecuador. 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec
